        class="heading">
          Objective
        </div>

        <div id="experiment-article-section-3-content" 
        class="content">
      <p>The following are the objectives of this series of assignments.</p>
	<ol>
	  <li>Learn Parameter and Return Value passing mechanism</li>
      <li>Using stack to pass parameters and store other state information.</li>
      <li>Know the distinction between a leaf and non-lead procedure.</li>
  </ol>

        </div>

      </section>


