          <div id="experiment-article-section-6-content" 
          class="content">
            
             <p>
	     <p>Implement the following C-procedures in ARM. You can assume the parameters are passed either in registers or through the stack.</p>
  <ol><li>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="code">swap(int *a, int *b)<br />
        {<br />
           &nbsp;&nbsp;int temp;<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;temp = *a;<br />
             &nbsp;&nbsp;*a = *b;<br />
              &nbsp; *b = temp;<br />
        }</p>
      </blockquote>
      </li>
      <li>
        <blockquote>Write a sorting routine with signature Sort(int *data, int dim) where dim gives the dimension of the array 'data'. Use the swap routine you have written earlier in the Sort routine.</blockquote>
      </li>
  </ol>
	    </p>

          </div>

